# `apps/docs` (`@proxed/docs`)

Docs site built with Next.js + Fumadocs.

## Entry points

- MDX content: `apps/docs/content/docs/*`
- App Router: `apps/docs/app/(docs)/...`
- Content source + metadata: `apps/docs/lib/*`
- Search indexing scripts: `apps/docs/scripts/*`

## Conventions

- Prefer editing existing MDX content instead of adding new doc systems.
- Keep MDX components centralized (see existing `apps/docs/lib/*` and `apps/docs/app/*` wiring).
- Avoid hardcoding external search provider details; use existing scripts/config.

